data.description:
2-story home that boasting a fully finished basement complete with a kitchenette.  With 4 spacious bedrooms upstairs, including the luxurious master suite, this home offers an abundance of space for your family to thrive.

The master suite features a private bathroom that offers both a standing shower and a relaxing jacuzzi tub. Additionally, the master suite comes equipped with a walk-in closet. Plus, there's a bonus room adjacent to the master suite, currently being used as a movie theater, making it an ideal space for entertainment and relaxation.

The first-floor laundry makes chores a breeze, and you'll find two cozy fireplaces within the home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere during colder months. Notably, the home has been upgraded with a new furnace, central air system, hot water tank, and water softener, all installed in 2023, ensuring comfort and energy efficiency.

Maintaining the exterior is made simple with an irrigation system, ensuring your yard stays lush and green year-round. The practicality of having an office or den on the first floor provides a quiet space for work or study, adding to the home's functionality.

This beautifully maintained property offers a seamless blend of luxury and convenience, with its modern amenities and thoughtful layout. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home your own, and enjoy the comfortable, stylish, and entertaining lifestyle it affords. It's a true gem in the real estate market.
